{"tid":288730,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【大雨警報】與低壓槽相關的雷雨正影響本港（2017/6/18）","createTime":"2017-06-18T11:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T00:37:56.000Z","uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35509da722fe488dce6fc69297f1ead3231f5b5c","tid":288730,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:49:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><img src=\"http://x.co/wk011\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk011&h=231cb168&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://x.co/wk012\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk012&h=31a91e86&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>大雨警報：2017年6月18日</ins></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">此帖文討論期：大雨影響完結為止</span></span></strong><br />\n【註】 發出大雨警報，表示本港大部分地區可能受持續大雨影響。　此帖文為短期性質，當取消大雨警報後會隨即停用。　為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。　請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在貼文上。謝謝。　以下圖片會自動更新。<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">氣象台專頁現已登場</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/FBlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FFBlike&h=5fdd3157&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://fb.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FHKGweather&d=XBtCiekKnBD61yqLsWuThNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=6addd190\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/TWlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FTWlike&h=e9b064ef&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGweather&d=XBtCiekKnBD61yqLsWuThNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=7eef2b09\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKGweather</a></span></em><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style