dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:01:13.000Z","msg":"已減弱"},{"pid":"3edb20ae149e65c5c8134eea2390462d20b2fcbf","tid":288730,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:24:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家影響香港果條低壓槽，是咪ITCZ黎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nitcz係赤道附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nITCZ會郁架wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n郁極都唔會離開熱帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家香港呢條係靜止鋒，<br />\n由北面黎既較冷空氣同跨洋而黎既暖西南氣流相撞抬升產雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nitcz係兩道信風帶抬升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外而家靜止鋒係香港以南，<br />\n所以而家香港天氣稍涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d15b856ff9ea387565035eeabac26cfadda206ba","tid":288730,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:53:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家影響香港果條低壓槽，是咪ITCZ黎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nitcz係赤道附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nITCZ會郁架wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n郁極都唔會離開熱帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家香港呢條係靜止鋒，<br />\n由北面黎既較冷空氣同跨洋而黎既暖西南氣流相撞抬升產雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nitcz係兩道信風帶抬升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外而家靜止鋒係香港以南，<br />\n所以而家香港天氣稍涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n低壓槽點解會向上<br />\n同係咪general 向下?"},{"pid":"c8c3a09ec6fcd5fb747909f63543a3d8316f7435","tid":288730,"uid":29063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T14:15:24.000Z","msg":"宜家條雨帶走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5f874d91f4c8f343ace20ba0747c451de32f60","tid":288730,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T14:49:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家影響香港果條低壓槽，是咪ITCZ黎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nitcz係赤道附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nITCZ會郁架wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n郁極都唔會離開熱帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家香港呢條係靜止鋒，<br />\n由北面黎既較冷空氣同跨洋而黎既暖西南氣流相撞抬升產雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nitcz係兩道信風帶抬升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外而家靜止鋒係香港以南，<br />\n所以而家香港天氣稍涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n低壓槽點解會向上<br />\n同係咪general 向下?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n靜止鋒又叫滯留鋒，會係一個地區附近滯留但未至於完全唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n北風稍強咪向下（南），南風稍強就向上（北）但槽移動速度好慢，所以雨區大致都係係差唔多位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同冷鋒見到成條雨帶狗衝落黎唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a05b835715537708359d4aa3a587b5fa62c6473","tid":288730,"uid":43,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"molamola"},{"pid":"c27e491de26e6a378a02e589c9e8f41c061ce458","tid":288730,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:04:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家影響香港果條低壓槽，是咪ITCZ黎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nitcz係赤道附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nITCZ會郁架wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n郁極都唔會離開熱帶<img src=\"/asset