"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同冷鋒見到成條雨帶狗衝落黎唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點睇咩風勁d<br />\n即係冷暖空氣各相當實力? 應該係睇到 ， 但點睇<br />\n<br />\n冬天係咪得冷鋒， 無靜止鋒?</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7dd5f107cffef70d9231116e6b9a436bb7d55a59","tid":288730,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:12:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家影響香港果條低壓槽，是咪ITCZ黎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nitcz係赤道附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nITCZ會郁架wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n郁極都唔會離開熱帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家香港呢條係靜止鋒，<br />\n由北面黎既較冷空氣同跨洋而黎既暖西南氣流相撞抬升產雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nitcz係兩道信風帶抬升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外而家靜止鋒係香港以南，<br />\n所以而家香港天氣稍涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n低壓槽點解會向上<br />\n同係咪general 向下?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n靜止鋒又叫滯留鋒，會係一個地區附近滯留但未至於完全唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n北風稍強咪向下（南），南風稍強就向上（北）但槽移動速度好慢，所以雨區大致都係係差唔多位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同冷鋒見到成條雨帶狗衝落黎唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點睇咩風勁d<br />\n即係冷暖空氣各相當實力? 應該係睇到 ， 但點睇<br />\n<br />\n好似冬天冷鋒咁， 而無靜止鋒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實出得靜止鋒就基本冷暖強度相若，但始終唔會exactly一樣，通常都係冷空氣一方稍佔優靜止鋒慢慢南下，然後暖濕反攻靜止鋒慢慢北上，尤其呢個季節暖濕會一直推到梅雨鋒（呢個時節既靜止鋒）去更北。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於點睇邊面勁d，其實睇條槽被推向邊，轉北風地區多定轉南風地區多，好似暫時北風佔優，廣東沿岸由南風轉左北風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd37c74779630b77f8ff7ec7e41dbe98ccad0f7f","tid":288730,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:14:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家影響香港果條低壓槽，是咪ITCZ黎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nitcz係赤道附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nITCZ會郁架wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n郁極都唔會離開熱帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家香港呢條係靜止鋒，<br />\n由北面黎既較冷空氣同跨洋而黎既暖西南氣流相撞抬升產雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nitcz係兩道信風帶抬升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外而家靜止鋒係香港以南，<br />\n所以而家香港天氣稍涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n低壓槽點解會向上<br />\n同係咪general 向下?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n靜止鋒又叫滯留鋒，會係一個地區附近滯留但未至於完全唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n北風稍強咪向下（南），南風稍強就向上（北）但槽移動速度好慢，所以雨區大致都係係差唔多位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同冷鋒見到成條雨帶狗衝落黎唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點睇咩風勁d<br />\n即係冷暖空氣各相當實力? 應該係睇到 ， 但點睇<br />\n<br />\n冬天係咪得冷鋒， 無靜止鋒?</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基本冬天係無靜止鋒，因為冷空氣強度係壓倒性既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有同冬天冷空氣相若強度既暖濕咁真係異常得好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703d3d052ba4b0a69d174398b3c3b4cdd1f1766c","tid":288730,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T00:37:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><img src=\"http://x.co/wk011\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk011&h=231cb168&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://x.co/wk012\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk012&h=31a91e86&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大雨警報</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>請在以下帖文集中討論大雨：</ins></span></span><br />\n【大雨警報】與低壓槽相關的雷雨正影響本港（2017/6/19）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/289279\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/289279</a></strong>"}]}